celeriac waffles

needs:
- 450g grated celeriac
- 2 eggs
- ½ tsp garlic granules
- ½ tsp onion granules
- ½ tsp salt
- ½ tsp ground black pepper

steps:
- heat the waffle iron and grease if necessary.
- combine all ingredients in a large bowl.
- dollop batter into the waffle iron (about ¼ cup or 60g per waffle).
- cook for 5 minutes.
